fr.jgetmove.jgetmove.database

Class DataBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.jgetmove.jgetmove.database.Base
      • fr.jgetmove.jgetmove.database.DataBase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PrettyPrint

    public class DataBase
extends Base
    Class containing all the basic data. Allows to bind the data from input files

    All the data is binded once, note that adding or rebinding data in here is expensive. Use ClusterMatrix for a dynamic database.

    Since:
    0.1.0
